<p>The Assistant Cook is an important part of your colonyâ€™s food production. The Assistant Cook will craft any food-related recipes you have taught the Restaurant if the <a href="../../source/workers/cook">Cook</a> requests food. They will also craft any craftable foods you requested from the <a href="../../source/items/postbox">postbox</a>.</p>

<p><strong>Note:</strong> You can only hire an Assistant Cook when the Restaurant is at least level 3.</p>
